column1: IF ccr_sa_thf_d is MF 2 AND ccr_llb_oh_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_ths_d is MF 1 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_dha_d is MF 1 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 0
IF ccr_cortisol_d is MF 1 AND ccr_tha_d is MF 0 AND ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 1 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 0  3_Surpoid is 1  4_Obese is 1  5_ExtremeObese is 0
